ml.alternet.security.auth.hashers.impl

Class MessageHasher

  • java.lang.Object
    • ml.alternet.security.auth.hashers.impl.HasherBase<CryptParts>
      • ml.alternet.security.auth.hashers.impl.MessageHasher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Credentials.Checker, Hasher

    public class MessageHasher
extends HasherBase<CryptParts>
    The hasher is based on Java's message digests. If the platform doesn't supply the expected message digest, the discovery service tries to find one with the algorithm name.
    Author:
    Philippe Poulard
    See Also:
    MessageDigest, MD4
